{"tid":2326238,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"福建「華龍一號」核反應堆試檢期間一度停運　無泄輻射","createTime":"2020-12-15T07:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T10:57:11.000Z","uid":48973,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d4955d803e97d5989f7afd8788e45f6cd03ff201","tid":2326238,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:44:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20201215/s00004/1608008393820/%e7%a6%8f%e5%bb%ba%e3%80%8c%e8%8f%af%e9%be%8d%e4%b8%80%e8%99%9f%e3%80%8d%e6%a0%b8%e5%8f%8d%e6%87%89%e5%a0%86%e8%a9%a6%e6%aa%a2%e6%9c%9f%e9%96%93%e4%b8%80%e5%ba%a6%e5%81%9c%e9%81%8b-%e7%84%a1%e6%b3%84%e8%bc%bb%e5%b0%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20201215%2Fs00004%2F1608008393820%2F%25e7%25a6%258f%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e3%2580%258c%25e8%258f%25af%25e9%25be%258d%25e4%25b8%2580%25e8%2599%259f%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%25a0%25b8%25e5%258f%258d%25e6%2587%2589%25e5%25a0%2586%25e8%25a9%25a6%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%259c%259f%25e9%2596%2593%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e5%2581%259c%25e9%2581%258b-%25e7%2584%25a1%25e6%25b3%2584%25e8%25bc%25bb%25e5%25b0%2584&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGL0p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=b54c5617\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20201215%2Fs00004%2F1608008393820%2F%25e7%25a6%258f%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e3%2580%258c%25e8%258f%25af%25e9%25be%258d%25e4%25b8%2580%25e8%2599%259f%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%25a0%25b8%25e5%258f%258d%25e6%2587%2589%25e5%25a0%2586%25e8%25a9%25a6%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%259c%259f%25e9%2596%2593%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e5%2581%259c%25e9%2581%258b-%25e7%2584%25a1%25e6%25b3%2584%25e8%25bc%25bb%25e5%25b0%2584&h=95bb340c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20201215/s00004/1608008393820/%e7%a6%8f%e5%bb%ba%e3%80%8c%e8%8f%af%e9%be%8d%e4%b8%80%e8%99%9f%e3%80%8d%e6%a0%b8%e5%8f%8d%e6%87%89%e5%a0%86%e8%a9%a6%e6%aa%a2%e6%9c%9f%e9%96%93%e4%b8%80%e5%ba%a6%e5%81%9c%e9%81%8b-%e7%84%a1%e6%b3%84%e8%bc%bb%e5%b0%84</a><br />\n<br />\n國家核安全局通報，10月27日，福建福清核電廠5號機組在執行蒸氣排放連鎖檢查試驗期間，機組自動停堆，定為零級運行事件。事發期間，人員操作未見明顯重大異常，<span class=\"medium\"><span class=\"red\">事件未造成放射性釋放，未對人員和環境安全造成不良影響。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n通報稱，國家核安全局於11月9至13日組織專家赴福清核電廠，對事件開展獨立調查。根據調查情況，本次事件的發生原因為：二迴路第二環路主蒸氣管道疏水管線逆止閥存在質量偏差導致卡着；營運單位缺乏疏水管線堵塞引發主蒸氣管道蒸氣、冷凝水相互作用複雜動態的相關知識和經驗，對疏水管線管控不足。<br />\n<br />\n中核集團福清核電廠5號機組使用的是<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">中國自主研製三代核電「華龍一號」全球首個核反應堆</span></span>，在11月27日首次併網成功。據官媒當時報道，經現場確認，該機組各項技術指標均符合設計要求，機組狀態良好，創造了全球第三代核電首堆建設的最佳業績。"},{"pid":"5d2993e0148c59b43e4fb330679bf0bd90193221","tid":2326238,"uid":48973,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:45:49.000Z","msg":"末日近了，你們應當悔改<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c4dc78b8308c765f7b8df0c5ea6a9e4e141a61","tid":2326238,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:50:36.000Z","msg":"核幅射對支那人無害<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74fde785f1ed227c06090fb6121c0ec868c8552","tid":2326238,"uid":48973,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:59:16.000Z","msg":"原來離台北250km以內 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n統一指日可待"},{"pid":"ab104ff2a023fcfa716ff00c4aba42f9b4d2783f","tid":2326238,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GfSYWW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGfSYWW4.jpg&h=dbb66b3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a1fee6e10a18ee33e9747913b61d11e7e39af2d","tid":2326238,"uid":259716,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab104ff2a023fcfa716ff00c4aba42f9b4d2783f","tid":2326238,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0